The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Cecelia Lederle, Appellant. The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Dan Castrillo, Appellant. The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Oscar Bickel, Appellant.

(Consolidated Appeals.)

Submitted July 8, 1955; decided July 8, 1955. Raymond Reran O’Brien for motion. No one opposed.

Motion granted and case set down for argument during the October, 1955, session of the Court of Appeals.
